      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔母上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00002",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "凄凉萧寺，空迤逦，故园不堪回首。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00003",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "雕笼不解藏鹦鹉，绣幕何须护海棠。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00004",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "这几日，窃见莺莺神思恍惚，不知为着何事。待我叫红娘出来，拷问一番，便知明白。红娘哪里，红娘哪里？",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00005",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "红娘上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00006",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "吓，来了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00007",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "若不是红娘引逗，怎能够两下来成就。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00008",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "红娘快来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00009",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住，今日老夫人为何怒气冲冲，在那里叫我，莫非此事发觉了。这便怎么处？啐，自古道丑媳妇，少不得要见公婆面的，就去何妨。",
      "text_length": 61
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00010",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "吓红娘。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00011",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "在这里。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00012",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "叫你半日，为何不来。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00013",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "老夫人叫红娘是就来的吓。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00014",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "与我跪下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00015",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "好端端的为何跪起来？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00016",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "还不跪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00017",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "要跪就跪。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00018",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "我且问你，每日同小姐，到后花园中干什么？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00019",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "叫我道着什么？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00020",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "唔。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00021",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "吓，是烧香的。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00022",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "烧什么香？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00023",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐说，若要萱堂增寿考，全凭早晚一炉香，可以保佑老夫人的。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00024",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "可有什么别事？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00025",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "没有吓。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00026",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "唔，你还瞒我。打死你这小贱人，小贱人吓！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00027",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "着你行监坐守，谁许你胡行乱走。一任你握雨携云，常使我提心在手。你花言巧语，你花言巧语，将没做有，使我出乖露丑。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00028",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "相府家，有什么出乖露丑？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00029",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "还要胡说，打死你这小贱人。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00030",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "吓哈打打你这贱丫头，不说出始末根由事，叫我如何索罢休。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00031",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "那日间，停刺绣，把此情穷究。道张——",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00032",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "“张”什么？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00033",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "张生病染沉疴。小姐说，要同我到书斋问候。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00034",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "张生有病，与你们什么相干？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00035",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "不但小姐不该去，连红娘也是不该去的。阿呀张生，你那天杀的。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00036",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "使红娘暂回，使红娘暂回。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00037",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "小姐呢？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00038",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐权——",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00039",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "“权”什么。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00040",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "待我说呢。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00041",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐权时落后。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00042",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "女孩儿家岂可落得后的？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00043",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "落后就落后，只管问。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00044",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "你不说，我就要打。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00045",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "老夫人不要打，待我说。女孩儿家落后有什么好处吓。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00046",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "完了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00047",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "桂枝香",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "想做了鸾交凤友。慢追求始末根由事，如何索罢休。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00048",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "我想此事，非怪张生、小姐、红娘之过，都是老夫人不是。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00049",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "怎么到是我不是？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00050",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "老夫人请坐，待红娘告禀。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00051",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "你说。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00052",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "我想信乃人之根本，人而无信，不知其可也。大车无輗，小车无軏，其何以行之哉。当初兵围普救寺的时节，老夫人有言：“如有退得贼兵者，愿将小女妻之”。可是有的？",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00053",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "是有的。此乃退兵之计。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00054",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "张生非慕小姐颜色，岂肯建此退兵之计？如今兵退身安，老夫人悔言失信。既不成其亲事，只合酬以金帛，令张生舍此而去，不合留于书院，相近咫尺，使怨女旷夫，早晚各相窥视，因而有此一端。老夫人若不早息此事，一来玷辱相国家声，二来张生名望有亏，既施恩于人，反受其辱。那官府推详此事，老夫人先有治家不严之罪，忘恩负义之愆。",
      "text_length": 153
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00055",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "如今呢？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00056",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "今据红娘看来，一些也不难。莫若赦其小过，成其大事，只滌其旧染之污，而自新，岂不为长便乎？",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00057",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "你这小贱人，倒说得干净。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00058",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "不干净，也不说了。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00059",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "退后。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00060",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00061",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "且住。我想家门不幸，养这不肖之女，我今若到官去，一来玷辱相国家声，二来张生名望有亏。咳，罢，不如依了这小贱人。过来，唤那禽兽过来。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00062",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "哪个什么禽兽吓？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00063",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "张生。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00064",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "我不去。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00065",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "为何不去？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00066",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "又道是红娘递书信去了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00067",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "哪个在，取家法过来。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00068",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "走走走，张生快来。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00069",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00070",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "来了，红娘姐。为何如此？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00071",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "好吓。你们快活，累我打得这般光景。如今叫你去做亲。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00072",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "怎生去见老夫人？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00073",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "你装做假道学，摇摇摆摆，过去就是了。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00074",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "自古沉舟可补，如今覆水难收。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00075",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "老夫人拜揖。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00076",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "张生，我何等样待你，如今干出这样事来。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00077",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "小生只此一遭。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00078",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "两遭，连外孙都有了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00079",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "胡说。唤那不肖的出来。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00080",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "小姐快来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00081",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔莺莺上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00082",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔莺莺"
      ],
      "text": "红娘怎么说？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00083",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "此事老夫人知道了，被我说长道短，讲了一番。如今叫你去做亲。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00084",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔莺莺"
      ],
      "text": "羞答答怎样前去？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00085",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "就照前日，见张生时的样儿就好。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00086",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔莺莺"
      ],
      "text": "母亲。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00087",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "张生，今日我就将莺莺许配与你。只是我家三代姻亲无白身者，我今赠你盘费，明日就起行赴京，求取功名。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00088",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "也要过了满月再去。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00089",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "什么满月？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00090",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "不过满月也要过了三朝。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00091",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "明日定要动身。倘能到京，得个一官半职，那时回来，也对得过我母女。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00092",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "多谢厚意。正是：",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00093",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "张珙"
      ],
      "text": "今日果然成凤侣，明朝又复唱丽歌。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00094",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张珙下，崔莺莺下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00095",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "吓老夫人，此事若不是我红娘调处，断难结此良缘。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00096",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "崔母"
      ],
      "text": "若无你这小贱人，还坏不了大事。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00097",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "崔母下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00098",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "红娘"
      ],
      "text": "总是我的不是。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01020012_e00099",
      "play_id": "01020012",
      "scene_id": "01020012_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "红娘下。",
      "text_length": 4
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}